OL,5, Thousands of postal workers at Royal   
OL,6, Mail are on strike over pay and        
OL,7, conditions, potentially causing        
OL,8, disruption to customers' festive       
OL,9, deliveries.                            
OL,11,FMore than 115,000 staff walked out on  
OL,12,FFriday, with more strikes to follow in 
OL,13,Fthe run-up to Christmas.               
OL,15,FRecent talks between the CWU union and 
OL,16,FRoyal Mail have broken down.           
OL,18,FMembers of the union are expected to   
OL,19,Fcontinue striking on Sunday as well as 
OL,20,Fon 14, 15, 23 and 24 December.         
